==Description==
The '''Star Piece''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Star Piece''' has a value of 5 Diamonds {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals. 

==Mine Layout==
The Star Piece appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
